WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
So where they kind of work really well together in the big picture is, you can do your development

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:10.040
inside of Posit Workbench using data that's governed and the compute that's in Databricks.

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:14.840
And then when you finally, or when you're done and you want to put this app, you know,

00:00:14.840 --> 00:00:18.200
make it available, you want to share it with other people, then you can use Posit Connect.

00:00:18.200 --> 00:00:21.879
And then sort of on the other side, this shiny app on Posit Connect is connected to Databricks

00:00:21.879 --> 00:00:25.000
and querying data, and that's governed and all that kind of stuff.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.959
So that's kind of like the two sides of it, Databricks is kind of in the middle.

